<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="features-header">
    <p class="section-eyebrow reveal">Technologie</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Conçu pour l'excellence.</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="features-grid">
    <div class="feature-card reveal">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="20" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <path d="M24 14v10l6 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Vitesse variable</h3>
      <p>Ajustez l'intensité selon vos besoins — du débutant au sportif intensif.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card reveal">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M8 24h6M34 24h6M24 8v6M24 34v6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
          <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>8 têtes interchangeables</h3>
      <p>Chaque embout cible une zone précise : dos, jambes, bras, cou, plante des pieds.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card reveal">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <rect x="16" y="8" width="16" height="32" rx="3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
          <path d="M20 36h8M22 8v-4h4v4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Charge USB-C</h3>
      <p>Une charge complète en 2h. Batterie longue durée pour plusieurs séances.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card reveal">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M12 36L24 12l12 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <path d="M16 28h16" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3>Ultra silencieux</h3>
      <p>Technologie brushless — puissant sans être bruyant. Utilisez-le partout.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

